                <note rend="inline" type="source">893.00/11698: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Consul General at Canton</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Ballantine</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Canton</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1931-12-31T11:00:00+08:00"
                            >December 31, 1931—11 a.m.</date>
                        <lb/>[Received December 31—2:30 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>I have just been informed authoritatively that the necessary order for the
                    dissolution of the National Government at Canton on January 1st is being issued
                    today.</p>
                <p>Repeated to Nanking, Legation at Peiping.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Ballantine</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
